<html>

<head>
    {{> header-head }}
</head>
<body>

<div id="app">
    {{> header-login }}

    <h1 align="center">Perry Rhodan English summaries</h1>

Here is a list of all the Perry Rhodan cycles along with the number of issues that have an English summary.
    If you recently read an issue that is not listed below, please submit a summary by entering its number
    in the text field below. Or you can ust that text field to directly jump to an existing summary.

    You can also subscribe to the
    <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/PerryRhodanSummaries">
        RSS feed
        <img src="http://beust.com/pics/feed-icon16x16.png"
             alt="http://feeds.feedburner.com/PerryRhodanSummaries" border="0"/></a>,
    <a href="http://twitter.com/PerryRhodanUS">follow us on Twitter</a>,
    or jump directly to an issue:

    <br/>

    <table align="center">
        <tr align="center">
            <td>
                <form action = "/summaries" method="get">
                    <input type="text" name="number"/><br>
                    <input type="submit" value="Show summary" />
                </form>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <p>
        Total number of summaries: {{summaryCount}} ({{percentage}} %)
    </p>

    <p>
        Latest summaries posted:
        <ul>
            {{#recentSummaries}}
                <li><a href="/summaries/{{number}}">{{number}}: {{englishTitle}}</a> ({{date}})</li>
            {{/recentSummaries}}
        </ul>
    </p>

    <table border="1" align="center" width="80%">
        <thead>
            <td>Number</td>
            <td>Issues</td>
            <td>German title</td>
            <td>English title</td>
            <td>Number of summaries</td>
            <td>Percentage completed</td>
        </thead>
        {{#cycles}}
        <tr>
            <td>{{number}}</td>
            <td>{{start}}-{{end}}</td>
            <td>{{germanTitle}}</td>
            <td><a href="{{href}}">{{englishTitle}}</a></td>
            <td>{{summaryCount}}</td>
            <td>{{percentage}}%</td>
        </tr>
        {{/cycles}}
    </table>

</div>

{{> footer }}
</body>
<html>

